    "name": {
      "zh": "柯尔特 M16A1E1 5.56x45 突击步枪上机匣",
      "en": "M16A1E1 5.56x45 upper receiver"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "M16A1E1",
      "en": "M16A1E1"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "柯尔特公司为 M16A1E1 突击步枪设计的专用上机匣。M16A1E1 (柯尔特 645 型) 是美国海军陆战队主导改进的 M16A1 升级型号，同时也是 M16A2 (柯尔特 701 型) 的前身，加拿大迪玛科公司同样以此为基础打造了 C7 步枪。这款机匣在上世纪 80 年代广泛见于柯尔特制造的多款特种卡宾枪上。",
      "en": "An upper receiver for the M16A1E1 assault rifle manufactured by Colt. An early prototype variant between the M16A1 and M16A2, which also served as the basis for the Canadian C7. During the 1980s it was widely fitted to various special carbines produced by Colt."
    },
